MST_SKILLS_2001172_NAME.vi: Không! Ta ko đc thất bại trong nhiệm vụ bảo vệ những người khác!

MST_SKILLS_2001173_NAME.en: Friend! Leave this to me and focus on stirring the ship!
MST_SKILLS_2001173_NAME.es: ¡Amigo! ¡Déjame esto a mí y concéntrate en el timón!
MST_SKILLS_2001173_NAME.id: Teman! Biar aku mengatasinya dan fokus mengemudikan kapal!
MST_SKILLS_2001173_NAME.pt: Amigo. Deixa isso comigo e preocupe-se com o navio!
MST_SKILLS_2001173_NAME.th: สหาย! มาให้ข้าจัดการและดูแลเรือนี้แทน!
MST_SKILLS_2001173_NAME.vi: Bạn bè! Để việc này cho ta và tập trung làm náo động con tàu đi!

MST_SKILLS_2001180_NAME.th: เบิร์นนิ่ง สปิริต

MST_SKILLS_2001181_NAME.en: You want my help? Hmph. Are you up for a test?
MST_SKILLS_2001181_NAME.es: ¿Quieres mi ayuda? Mmm. ¿Te preparaste para esta prueba?
MST_SKILLS_2001181_NAME.id: Kau mau bantuanku? Hmph. Kau siap diuji?
MST_SKILLS_2001181_NAME.pt: Você quer minha ajuda? Humpf. Topa um teste?
MST_SKILLS_2001181_NAME.th: ต้องการให้ข้าช่วย? หืม เจ้าอยู่ในการทดสอบนี่?
MST_SKILLS_2001181_NAME.vi: Ngươi muốn ta giúp? Hừm. Ngươi đang thử làm gì vậy?

MST_SKILLS_2001182_NAME.en: You don't underestimate your enemies, do you?
MST_SKILLS_2001182_NAME.es: No subestimas a tus enemigos, ¿o sí?
MST_SKILLS_2001182_NAME.pt: Você não subestima seus inimigos, não é?
MST_SKILLS_2001182_NAME.th: เจ้าคงไม่ประเมินศัตรูต่ำเกินไปหรอกนะ?
MST_SKILLS_2001182_NAME.vi: Ngươi không đánh giá thấp kẻ thù của mình đó chứ?

MST_SKILLS_2001183_NAME.en: Well then. One strike will decide everything!
MST_SKILLS_2001183_NAME.id: Baiklah. Satu serangan akan memutuskan segalanya!
MST_SKILLS_2001183_NAME.pt: Muito bem. Um golpe decidirá tudo!
MST_SKILLS_2001183_NAME.th: เอาล่ะ ในการโจมตีนี้จะตัดสินทุกอย่าง!
MST_SKILLS_2001183_NAME.vi: Được thôi Một đòn sẽ quyết định tất cả!

MST_SKILLS_2001184_NAME.en: You're weak! Don't forget to prepare against attacks!
MST_SKILLS_2001184_NAME.es: ¡Eres débil! ¡No olvides prepararte para los ataques!
MST_SKILLS_2001184_NAME.id: Kau lemah! Jangan lupa bersiap melawan serangan!
MST_SKILLS_2001184_NAME.pt: Você é fraco! Não se esqueça de preparar suas defesas!
MST_SKILLS_2001184_NAME.th: เจ้าคนอ่อนแอ! อย่าลืมเตรียมตอบโต้กลับด้วยล่ะ!
MST_SKILLS_2001184_NAME.vi: Ngươi thật yếu ớt! Đừng quên chuẩn bị chống lại các đợt tấn công!

MST_SKILLS_2001190_NAME.th: โซลิด ไอซ์

MST_SKILLS_2001191_NAME.th: เจ้าต้องการบางอย่างจากข้าใช่มั้ย?
MST_SKILLS_2001191_NAME.vi: Ngươi muốn gì ở ta sao?

MST_SKILLS_2001192_NAME.en: So, you're trying your best now. Good job.
MST_SKILLS_2001192_NAME.es: Así que ahora estás dando todo de ti. Buen trabajo.
MST_SKILLS_2001192_NAME.id: Jadi, kamu mencoba sekuat tenaga sekarang. Bagus.
MST_SKILLS_2001192_NAME.pt: Então, está se esforçando agora. Bom trabalho.
MST_SKILLS_2001192_NAME.th: งั้น ตอนนี้ก็ทำดีที่สุดแล้ว เยี่ยม
MST_SKILLS_2001192_NAME.vi: Vậy, giờ ngươi hãy cố hết sức đi. Tốt lắm.

MST_SKILLS_2001193_NAME.en: Wow, you're better than I thought.
MST_SKILLS_2001193_NAME.es: Guau, eres mejor de lo que esperaba.
MST_SKILLS_2001193_NAME.id: Wah, kamu lebih baik dari yang kupikir.
MST_SKILLS_2001193_NAME.pt: Nossa, você é melhor do que eu esperava.
MST_SKILLS_2001193_NAME.th: ว้าว เจ้าเก่งกว่าที่ข้าคิดไว้นะเนี่ย
MST_SKILLS_2001193_NAME.vi: Wow, ngươi khá hơn là ta nghĩ đấy.

MST_SKILLS_2001194_NAME.en: What burdens do you carry on your shoulders?
MST_SKILLS_2001194_NAME.id: Beban apa yang kamu tanggung di pundakmu?
MST_SKILLS_2001194_NAME.th: อะไรที่เจ้าแบกไว้เป็นภาระ?
MST_SKILLS_2001194_NAME.vi: Ngươi đang mang gánh nặng gì trên vai mình vậy?

MST_SKILLS_20011_DESCRIPTION.en: 4 combo Water elemental attack on all enemies
MST_SKILLS_20011_DESCRIPTION.es: Combo grupal de 4 ataques de agua.
MST_SKILLS_20011_DESCRIPTION.id: 4 kombo serangan berelemen Air pada semua Musuh
MST_SKILLS_20011_DESCRIPTION.pt: Combo de 4 golpes com elemento Água em todos os inimigos
MST_SKILLS_20011_DESCRIPTION.th: 4 คอมโบ ธาตุน้ำ โจมตีใส่ศัตรูทุกตัว
MST_SKILLS_20011_DESCRIPTION.vi: 12 cú Hỏa công mạnh mẽ lên mọi kẻ thù, thêm cơ hội bỏ qua Phòng thủ của đối thủ khi tấn công cho mọi đồng minh trong 2 lượt & tăng thiệt hại do đòn trí mạng trong 3 lượt cho tất cả đồng minh

MST_SKILLS_20011_NAME.th: อีเธียเรียลเบลด

MST_SKILLS_2001200_NAME.th: ไลท์นิ่ง แอโร่ว

MST_SKILLS_2001201_NAME.en: How dare you treat Lady Edea in such a manner!!
MST_SKILLS_2001201_NAME.es: ¡¿Cómo te atreves a tratar a Lady Edea de esa manera?!
MST_SKILLS_2001201_NAME.id: Kamu lancang berani memperlakukan Putri Edea seperti itu!!
MST_SKILLS_2001201_NAME.pt: Como se atreve a tratar Lady Edea desse jeito!!
MST_SKILLS_2001201_NAME.th: เจ้ากล้าดูแลท่านอีเดียด้วยวิธีแบบนี้เรอะ!!
MST_SKILLS_2001201_NAME.vi: Sao ngươi dám đối xử với Tiểu thư Edea như vậy!!

MST_SKILLS_2001202_NAME.th: ประกาศตัวออกมา!

MST_SKILLS_2001203_NAME.en: Lady Edea! Don't place your trust in that person!
MST_SKILLS_2001203_NAME.id: Putri Edea! Jangan percaya pada orang itu!
MST_SKILLS_2001203_NAME.pt: Lady Edea! Não confie nessa pessoa!
MST_SKILLS_2001203_NAME.th: ท่านอีเดีย!อย่าไว้ใจคนผู้นั้นให้มากนักเลย!
MST_SKILLS_2001203_NAME.vi: Tiểu thư Edea! Đừng tin tưởng kẻ đó!

MST_SKILLS_2001204_NAME.en: Ngh... I couldn't prove my strength, but--!
MST_SKILLS_2001204_NAME.es: Ngh... ¡No pude probar mi fuerza, pero...!
MST_SKILLS_2001204_NAME.id: Ngh… Aku tidak bisa membuktikan kekuatanku, tapi--!
MST_SKILLS_2001204_NAME.pt: Ngh... Não pude provar minha força, mas--!
MST_SKILLS_2001204_NAME.th: ชิ...ถึงข้าจะพิสูจน์ความแข็งแกร่งของตัวเองไม่ได้ แต่--!
MST_SKILLS_2001204_NAME.vi: Ngh... Ta không thể chứng minh sức mạnh của mình, nhưng--!

MST_SKILLS_2001210_NAME.th: ไดมอนด์ ดัส

MST_SKILLS_2001211_NAME.en: Loch, let's train before our big battle tomorrow!
MST_SKILLS_2001211_NAME.es: ¡Loch, entrenemos antes de nuestra gran batalla de mañana!
MST_SKILLS_2001211_NAME.id: Loch, ayo berlatih sebelum perang besar kita besok!
MST_SKILLS_2001211_NAME.pt: Loch, vamos treinar antes de nossa grande batalha amanhã!
MST_SKILLS_2001211_NAME.th: ล็อค จงฝึกฝนไว้ก่อนการต่อสู้ครั้งใหญ่ในวันพรุ่งนี้!
MST_SKILLS_2001211_NAME.vi: Loch, hãy tập luyện trước trận chiến lớn ngày mai!

MST_SKILLS_2001212_NAME.en: Loch, if you don't hit your target, Edea will get mad!
MST_SKILLS_2001212_NAME.es: ¡Loch, si no golpeas a tu objetivo, Edea se enfurecerá!
MST_SKILLS_2001212_NAME.id: Loch, kalau kamu tidak tepat sasaran, Edea akan marah!
MST_SKILLS_2001212_NAME.pt: Loch, se você não acertar o alvo, Edea vai ficar brava!
MST_SKILLS_2001212_NAME.th: ล็อค ถ้าเจ้ากำจัดเป้าหมายไม่ได้ อีเดียต้องโกรธแน่!
MST_SKILLS_2001212_NAME.vi: Loch, nếu anh không đánh trúng mục tiêu, Edea sẽ phát điên!

MST_SKILLS_2001213_NAME.en: Nice job! Guess you're not just a boy anymore.
MST_SKILLS_2001213_NAME.es: ¡Buen trabajo! Parece que ya has dejado de ser un niño.
MST_SKILLS_2001213_NAME.id: Bagus! Kurasa kamu bukan lagi seorang bocah.
MST_SKILLS_2001213_NAME.pt: Belo trabalho! Acho que você não é mais um menino.
MST_SKILLS_2001213_NAME.th: เยี่ยม! เจ้าไม่ใช่เด็กน้อยอีกต่อไปแล้ว
MST_SKILLS_2001213_NAME.vi: Hay lắm! Tôi đoán anh không còn là cậu bé nữa.

MST_SKILLS_2001214_NAME.en: What's wrong, Loch? All bark and no bite?
MST_SKILLS_2001214_NAME.id: Apa yang salah, Loch? Cuman mengonggong tanpa menggigit?
MST_SKILLS_2001214_NAME.pt: O que houve, Loch? Daqueles que late e não morde?
MST_SKILLS_2001214_NAME.th: เป็นอะไรไปล็อค? ดีแต่ปากรึไง?
MST_SKILLS_2001214_NAME.vi: Có vấn đề gì thế, Loch? Toàn kêu gào chẳng đánh đấm được gì?

MST_SKILLS_2001220_NAME.th: พัลซาร์ ฟอล

MST_SKILLS_2001221_NAME.en: Hmph. There's no way I'm training with you.
MST_SKILLS_2001221_NAME.es: Mmm. No hay manera de que yo entrene contigo.
MST_SKILLS_2001221_NAME.id: Hmph. Aku gak mungkin berlatih denganmu.
MST_SKILLS_2001221_NAME.pt: Humpf. Nunca que vou treinar com você.
MST_SKILLS_2001221_NAME.th: หืม ไม่มีทางที่ข้าจะฝึกกับเจ้า
MST_SKILLS_2001221_NAME.vi: Hừm. Tôi không đời nào tập luyện với anh.

MST_SKILLS_2001222_NAME.en: Dean, get out of my way! I can't aim right!
MST_SKILLS_2001222_NAME.es: ¡Dean, sal de mi camino! ¡No puedo apuntar bien!
MST_SKILLS_2001222_NAME.id: Dean, minggir! Aku tidak bisa membidik dengan benar!
MST_SKILLS_2001222_NAME.pt: Dean, sai do meu caminho! Não posso mirar direito!
MST_SKILLS_2001222_NAME.th: ท่าน อย่ามาขางทางข้า! ข้าเล็งไม่ได้!
MST_SKILLS_2001222_NAME.vi: Dean, tránh ra! Tôi không thể nhắm trúng!

MST_SKILLS_2001223_NAME.en: Dean, I have to admit, you are pretty strong.
MST_SKILLS_2001223_NAME.es: Dean, tengo que admitir que eres bastante fuerte.
MST_SKILLS_2001223_NAME.id: Dean, aku harus mengakui kamu lumayan kuat.
MST_SKILLS_2001223_NAME.pt: Dean, preciso admitir, você é bem forte.
MST_SKILLS_2001223_NAME.th: ขอขอยอมรับท่าน ท่านช่างแข็งแกร่งจริงๆ
MST_SKILLS_2001223_NAME.vi: Dean, tôi phải thừa nhận, anh khá mạnh.

MST_SKILLS_2001224_NAME.en: You just got in the way. Tomorrow I'll fight by myself.
MST_SKILLS_2001224_NAME.es: Te metiste en mi camino. Mañana pelearé por mí mismo.
MST_SKILLS_2001224_NAME.id: Kamu hanya menghalangiku. Besok aku bertarung sendirian.
MST_SKILLS_2001224_NAME.pt: Você só atrapalhou. Amanhã vou lutar sozinho.
MST_SKILLS_2001224_NAME.th: เพราะเจ้าเข้ามายุ่ง พรุ่งนี้ข้าจะสู้เอง
MST_SKILLS_2001224_NAME.vi: Anh chỉ cản đường thôi. Ngày mai tôi sẽ tự chiến đấu.

MST_SKILLS_2001230_NAME.th: ฮิดเดน ไดเมนชั่น

MST_SKILLS_2001231_NAME.th: ฟอเรนจ์ ไลท์

MST_SKILLS_2001233_NAME.en: Knowing you're no match for a god, you still defy me?
MST_SKILLS_2001233_NAME.es: Sabes que no eres rival para un dios y ¿osas desafiarme?
MST_SKILLS_2001233_NAME.id: Tahu kamu tidak bisa menyamai dewa, kamu masih melawanku?
MST_SKILLS_2001233_NAME.pt: Sabendo que você não é páreo para um deus, ainda me desafia?
MST_SKILLS_2001233_NAME.th: เมื่อเจ้ารู้ว่าไม่คู่ควรกับเทพ แล้วเจ้ายังจะปฏิเสธข้ารึ?
MST_SKILLS_2001233_NAME.vi: Biết ko phải đ.thủ của 1 vị thần mà ngươi vẫn thách ta sao?

MST_SKILLS_2001234_NAME.es: Los humanos sí que son criaturas torpes...
MST_SKILLS_2001234_NAME.id: Manusia memang adalah makhluk yang bodoh…
MST_SKILLS_2001234_NAME.th: มนุษย์เป็นสิ่งมีชีวิตที่โง่เง่าเสียจริง...
MST_SKILLS_2001234_NAME.vi: Con người quả là những sinh vật ngu ngốc thực sự...

MST_SKILLS_2001235_NAME.en: ...thinking they can destroy us with their power.
MST_SKILLS_2001235_NAME.es: ...piensan que pueden destruirnos con su poder.
MST_SKILLS_2001235_NAME.id: …berpikir mereka bisa melawan kita dengan kekuatan mereka.
MST_SKILLS_2001235_NAME.pt: ...achando que podem nos destruir com seu poder.
MST_SKILLS_2001235_NAME.th: ...คิดว่าจะกำจัดพวกเราได้ด้วยพลังของตัวเอง
MST_SKILLS_2001235_NAME.vi: ...nghĩ chúng có thể t.diệt bọn ta với sức mạnh của chúng.

MST_SKILLS_2001236_NAME.en: There is nothing left for you to protect.
MST_SKILLS_2001236_NAME.es: Ya no te queda nada que proteger.
MST_SKILLS_2001236_NAME.id: Tidak ada lagi yang bisa kamu lindungi.
MST_SKILLS_2001236_NAME.pt: Não sobrou nada para você proteger.
MST_SKILLS_2001236_NAME.th: ไม่มีอะไรให้เจ้าต้องปกป้องอีกต่อไป
MST_SKILLS_2001236_NAME.vi: Không còn gì để ngươi bảo vệ cả.

MST_SKILLS_2001237_NAME.en: You should surrender. Humans cannot defeat gods.
MST_SKILLS_2001237_NAME.es: Deberías rendirte. Los humanos no pueden derrotar a los dioses.
MST_SKILLS_2001237_NAME.id: Kamu lebih baik menyerah. Manusia tak bisa melawan dewa.
MST_SKILLS_2001237_NAME.pt: Você devia se render. Humanos não podem derrotar deuses.
MST_SKILLS_2001237_NAME.th: เจ้าควรจะยอมแพ้ซะ มนุษย์กำจัดเทพไม่ได้หรอก
MST_SKILLS_2001237_NAME.vi: Ngươi nên đầu hàng. Con người không thể đánh bại các vị thần.

MST_SKILLS_2001238_NAME.en: Could it be...that you're trying to seal me away?!
MST_SKILLS_2001238_NAME.pt: Será que... você está tentando me selar??
MST_SKILLS_2001238_NAME.th: หรือว่าเจ้า...คิดจะผนึกข้า?!
MST_SKILLS_2001238_NAME.vi: Có lẽ nào...ngươi đang cố gắng phong ấn ta?!

MST_SKILLS_2001240_NAME.th: แกรนด์ ครอส

MST_SKILLS_2001241_NAME.en: Great land of Palmyna, please lend us your power!
MST_SKILLS_2001241_NAME.es: ¡Gran tierra de Palmyna, por favor concédenos tu poder!
MST_SKILLS_2001241_NAME.id: Tanah Palmyna yang agung, pinjamkan kami kekuatanmu!
MST_SKILLS_2001241_NAME.pt: Grande terra de Palmyna, dê-nos seu poder!
MST_SKILLS_2001241_NAME.th: ดินแดนอันยิ่งใหญ่แห่งพัลมีน่า โปรดให้ข้ายืมพลังด้วย!
MST_SKILLS_2001241_NAME.vi: Đất mẹ Palmyna vĩ đại, hãy cho con mượn s.mạnh của người!

MST_SKILLS_2001242_NAME.en: Loch is in trouble! I have to--!
MST_SKILLS_2001242_NAME.th: ล็อคกำลังแย่! ข้าต้อง--!
MST_SKILLS_2001242_NAME.vi: Loch đang gặp rắc rối! Tôi phải--!

MST_SKILLS_2001243_NAME.en: Lafdranya, give me the power to protect everyone!
MST_SKILLS_2001243_NAME.es: ¡Lafdranya, dame el poder para proteger a todos!
MST_SKILLS_2001243_NAME.id: Lafdranya, berikan aku kekuatan untuk melindungi semua!
MST_SKILLS_2001243_NAME.pt: Lafdranya, dê-me o poder para proteger a todos!
MST_SKILLS_2001243_NAME.th: ลาฟดรานย่า ให้ข้ายืมพลังเพื่อปกป้องทุกคนด้วย!
MST_SKILLS_2001243_NAME.vi: Lafdranya, hãy cho tôi sức mạnh để bảo vệ mọi người!

MST_SKILLS_2001244_NAME.en: Even if it means relinquishing my own life...
MST_SKILLS_2001244_NAME.es: Incluso si eso significa renunciar a mi propia vida...
MST_SKILLS_2001244_NAME.pt: Mesmo se isso significa entregar minha vida...
MST_SKILLS_2001244_NAME.th: แม้จะหมายถึงการสละชีวิตของข้าก็ตาม...
MST_SKILLS_2001244_NAME.vi: Ngay cả khi điều đó có nghĩa là từ bỏ cuộc sống riêng...

MST_SKILLS_2001245_NAME.en: Professor! I will switch to the vanguard!
MST_SKILLS_2001245_NAME.id: Profesor! Aku akan maju ke garis depan!
MST_SKILLS_2001245_NAME.pt: Professor! Vou trocar para a vanguarda!
MST_SKILLS_2001245_NAME.th: ศาสตราจารย์! ข้าจะย้ายไปอยู่กองหน้า!
MST_SKILLS_2001245_NAME.vi: Giáo sư! Tôi sẽ chuyển sang đội tiên phong!

MST_SKILLS_2001246_NAME.th: ดีน ตั้งสมาธิอยู่กับเทคนิคของเจ้าสิ!
MST_SKILLS_2001246_NAME.vi: Dean, hãy tập trung vào các kỹ thuật của mình!

MST_SKILLS_2001247_NAME.th: ล็อค ถอยไป!

MST_SKILLS_2001250_NAME.th: เบลซซิ่ง สปิริต

MST_SKILLS_2001251_NAME.th: ศาสตราจารย์ ล็อค! ตามข้ามา!
MST_SKILLS_2001251_NAME.vi: Dean, Loch! Hãy theo chỉ dẫn của tôi!

MST_SKILLS_2001252_NAME.en: Don't assume that this is the extent of my power!
MST_SKILLS_2001252_NAME.es: ¡No asumas que este es todo mi poder!
MST_SKILLS_2001252_NAME.id: Jangan berasumsi ini adalah batas kekuatanku!
MST_SKILLS_2001252_NAME.pt: Não ache que meu poder é só isso!
MST_SKILLS_2001252_NAME.th: อย่าคิดไปเองสิว่าพลังของข้ามีแค่นี้!
MST_SKILLS_2001252_NAME.vi: Đừng cho rằng đây là phạm vi quyền lực của tôi!

MST_SKILLS_2001253_NAME.en: Young man! Now's not the time for your chatter!
MST_SKILLS_2001253_NAME.id: Anak muda! Sekarang bukan saatnya ngobrol!
